        0xF143 (61763 decimal) - Address_Alias_Resolution.

        0xF243 (62019 decimal) - Mosaic_Alias_Resolution.

      • TRANSACTION_GROUP

        public static final ReceiptType TRANSACTION_GROUP
        A collection of state changes for a given source. It is recorded when a state change receipt is issued.

        0xE134 (57652 decimal) - Transaction_Group.

      • MOSAIC_RENTAL_FEE

        public static final ReceiptType MOSAIC_RENTAL_FEE

        0x124D (4685 decimal) - Mosaic_Rental_Fee.

      • NAMESPACE_RENTAL_FEE

        public static final ReceiptType NAMESPACE_RENTAL_FEE
        The sender and recipient of the mosaicId and amount representing the cost of extending the namespace. It is recorded when a namespace is registered or its duration is extended.

        0x134E (4942 decimal) - Namespace_Rental_Fee.

      • LOCK_HASH_COMPLETED

        public static final ReceiptType LOCK_HASH_COMPLETED

        0x2248 (8776 decimal) - LockHash_Completed.

      • LOCK_HASH_CREATED

        public static final ReceiptType LOCK_HASH_CREATED

      • INFLATION

        public static final ReceiptType INFLATION
        The amount of native currency mosaics created. The receipt is recorded when the network has inflation configured, and a new block triggers the creation of currency mosaics.

        0x5143 (20803 decimal) - Inflation.
